query: SELECT u.id, u.name, u.email, COUNT(DISTINCT ce.id) as bundle_count FROM users u INNER JOIN course_enrollments ce ON u.id = ce.userId WHERE ce.bundleId IS NOT NULL GROUP BY u.id, u.name, u.email;
